Thursday,
May 1

Builders Day

FarCon

Thursday, May 1, 2025

8:30am – 9:00pm ET

Builders Day is a 24-hour hackathon, running from 8:30 AM on May 1 through 8:30 AM on May 2 (the start of The Summit). Hackers will need to submit their projects on the dedicated FarHack portal by 8:30 AM on May 2 in order to be considered for bounties and prizes.

The Merkle team will kick off Builders Day with a "mini Dev Day" from 10 AM - 12 PM. The rest of the day (12 PM - 9 PM) is dedicated to open hacking time and "office hours" with FarHack mentors.

Applications closed
